Package: modifiedfisher
Title: Non-Randomised Non-Conservative Size-Alpha Modified Fisher Exact Test
Description: Implements the non-randomised, non-conservative, size-alpha
    modified Fisher exact test of van der Meulen, Raymond, and van der Meulen (2021)
    <doi:10.13140/RG.2.2.34661.73448>, with agreeing test-based p-values,
    confidence intervals, and power. Controls the type I error rate
    while improving on the conservativeness of the standard Fisher
    exact test, and is compared against Woolf's asymptotic test and
    the fully randomised uniformly most powerful unbiased test.
URL: https://github.com/pvdmeulen/modifiedfisher, https://pvdmeulen.github.io/modifiedfisher/
BugReports: https://github.com/pvdmeulen/modifiedfisher/issues
